data.description: 3-bedroom 2.5 bath two story home.  Cul-de-sac lot.  Amazing space - 3024 sq ft!!  Main level LH new.  Granite counter tops and tons of cabinets in the kitchen.  Cozy fireplace in the great room.  Master bedroom has walk-in closet. Large bathroom.  Huge loft.  Fenced backyard.  Pond view.  This home needs a little TLC.  Please overlook toys.  Great home!  Huge loft couild be made into 4th bedroom easily.
